### Create root category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jewellery",
  "displayOrder": 1
}

### Create child category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gold Plated",
  "parentId": 1,
  "displayOrder": 1
}

### Create grandchild
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Necklaces",
  "parentId": 2,
  "displayOrder": 1
}

### Get tree
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
